items.sentence: Tom didn\'t even notice Mary was looking at him.
Tom didn\'t expect that Mary would outsmart him.
Tom didn\'t forget to do his homework this time.
Tom didn\'t give Mary his real telephone number.
Tom didn\'t give me the information I requested.
Tom wasn\'t able to do anything he needed to do.
Tom wasn\'t able to help Mary with her homework.
Tom turned right when he should\'ve turned left.
We often watch TV while we\'re eating breakfast.
Tom was touched that Mary was worried about him.
